videos.headline: Western Michigan takes pick-six 85 yards to the house
videos.description: Central Michigan's drive is quickly halted as Western Michigan cornerback Darius Phillips jumps the route and takes the interception 85 yards for the touchdown to give the Broncos a 35-3 lead.
